  "html": "<h3 id=\"tldr\">TL;DR</h3><p>In 2023, ReFi DAO supported the incubation of 'ReFi Local Nodes' globally, serving as innovative hubs for local regeneration. &nbsp;From Cape Town to Medellín, and with projects ranging from community engagement to environmental and technological advancements, each is charting a unique course towards ecological and social regeneration.</p><p>It’s time to look at the impact this network has generated during 2023. ⬇️</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read the full article on Mirror 📰</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Regenerative Journeys: ReFi Local Nodes 2023</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">🌱 Discover the Regenerative Finance revolution: How ReFi DAO is transforming communities worldwide for social and ecological harmony.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://mirror.xyz/favicon.ico\" alt=\"\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://images.mirror-media.xyz/nft/NciUmo2_K0HVUrpyf5PDy.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"><a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/01/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2023---2-.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1105\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2024/01/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2023---2-.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2024/01/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2023---2-.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/imag