\">ReFi Venezuela</a> <br>🇦🇹 <a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU#heading-refi-wien\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ReFi Wien</a> <br>🇸🇬 <a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU#heading-refi-singapore\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ReFi Singapore</a> <br>🇹🇷 <a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU#heading-refi-istanbul\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ReFi Istanbul</a> <br>🎉 <a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU#heading-refi-dao-global-2024---whats-next\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Conclusion</a>: ReFi DAO Global 2024 - What’s Next?</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read the full article on Mirror 📰</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/pzwS5ape0Zqu5mnqKM60eIqMfBtLjQ18UEy1jiDeAHU\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Regenerative Journeys: ReFi Local Nodes 2023</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">🌱 Discover the Regenerative Finance revolution: How ReFi DAO is transforming communities worldwide for social and ecological harmony.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://mirror.xyz/favicon.ico\" alt=\"\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://images.mirror-media.xyz/nft/NciUmo2_K0HVUrpyf5PDy.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><p><em>We would be super grateful if you might consider collecting this article as a piece of ReFi history or further support ReFi DAO publications by minting the custom NFT on Mirror</em> 👇 </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/nft/0x79222b9B9fAf4725D74b19C394Ea7135A0ca7d69/0\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Mint the NFT 🎨</a></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://mirror.xyz/0x7340F1a1e4e38F43d2FCC85cdb2b764de36B40c0/nft/0x79222b9B9fAf4725D74b19C394Ea7135A0ca7d69/0\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi on Mirror.xyz</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">Created by ReFi DAO</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://mirror.xyz/icon/favicon.svg\" alt=\"\"></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/inR3gu_Crna4IX8eQ8lSd.png?height=2790&amp;width=2790\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><hr><h1 id=\"refi-dao-global-2024what%E2%80%99s-next\">ReFi DAO Global 2024 - What’s Next?</h1><p>In 2024, ReFi DAO will focus on expanding its network, with the Local Node Beta Cohort launch as a key step. This initiative will provide nodes with enhanced tools and collaboration opportunities. Experienced founders and community builders are encouraged to apply and start their journey with the <a href=\"https://tally.so/r/mK5VYM\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ReFi DAO Local Node Beta Cohort Application Form</a>. Apply now! 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe src=\"https://tally.so/embed/mK5VYM?hideTitle=1&amp;alignLeft=1\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" title=\"Tally Forms\" scrolling=\"auto\"></iframe><script>var d=document,w=\"https://tally.so/widgets/embed.js\",v=function(){\"undefined\"!=typeof Tally?Tally.loadEmbeds():d.querySelectorAll(\"iframe[data-tally-src]:not([src])\").forEach((function(e){e.src=e.dataset.tallySrc}))};if(\"undefined\"!=typeof Tally)v();else if(d.querySelector('script[src=\"'+w+'\"]')==null){var s=d.createElement(\"script\");s.src=w,s.onload=v,s.onerror=v,d.body.appendChild(s);}</script></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://tally.so/r/mK5VYM\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Apply to become a local node!</a></div><p>Applications so far have been overwhelmingly positive, with a myriad of new nodes proposed from diverse locations like Sao Paulo, Santa Barbara, Uganda, Goma, Kuala Lumpur, and many more stepping forward to join the network.&nbsp;Current node leaders and applicants should also join the <a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Local-Nodes-2024Kickoff\" rel=\"noreferrer\">kickoff event for the Beta Incubator and Collaboration Circles</a> and stay informed about all <a href=\"https://lu.ma/refidao\" rel=\"noreferrer\">ReFi DAO Global events</a>, including the Beta Incubator and Collaboration Circles Kickoff, at the link below 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://lu.ma/refidao\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">ReFi DAO Global Events · Luma</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\">View and subscribe to events from ReFi DAO Global Events on Luma.</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://lu.ma/apple-touch-icon.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Subscribe</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://social-images.lu.ma/api/calendar-social-image?calendar_avatar_url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.lumacdn.com%2Fcalendars%2F6y%2F35b392f0-8e71-48dc-9082-1069afb078a5&amp;calendar_geo_city&amp;calendar_name=ReFi%20DAO%20Global%20Events&amp;calendar_tint_color=%23325ffa\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><p>As we advance into 2024, every new and existing node plays a vital role in our quest for a regenerative future. We're not just envisioning a world where finance benefits all; we're actively constructing it. Join us on this journey as we forge a thriving, fair, and regenerative world. 🎉🌍🌱</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2024/01/Ja7mV_sI8Wan58GuPXb9mvvv.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1123\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2024/01/Ja7mV_sI8Wan58GuPXb9mvvv.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2024/01/Ja7mV_sI8Wan58GuPXb9mvvv.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2024/01/Ja7mV_sI8Wan58GuPXb9mvvv.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2024/01/Ja7mV_sI8Wan58GuPXb9mvvv.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure>",
